column5: I'm looking for a drive to destination somewhere North of Wawa Ontario. Eater Walleyes and big Smallmouth are my target species. Three in our party. Thanks for any recommendations.
Air-Dale LodgeHappy Day LodgePrairie Bee CampWabatong LodgeLoch Island LodgeMurray Lake CottagesNorthern Walleye LodgeSent from my SM-A530W using Tapatalk
Just posted a reply to info on Como Lake check it out, it 's about 20 minutes west of Chapleau and just inside the Crown Wildlife Preserve. About 100 miles north of the Soo
